@startuml BE2

actor "Government Administrator" as Admin
participant "Dashboard" as Dash
participant "API Facade" as API
participant "Alert Management" as AlertMgmt
participant "Validation Service" as Validation
participant "Threshold Manager" as Thresh
participant "Data Analyst" as Analyst
participant "Algorithm Service" as Algo
participant "Recommendation Service" as Rec
participant "Sensor Company Rep" as SensorRep
database "Alert DB" as DB
participant "Audit Log" as Audit

Admin -> Dash : Access dashboard
Dash -> API : Send request
API -> AlertMgmt : Forward request

AlertMgmt -> Validation : Validate threshold data
Validation --> AlertMgmt : Validation result

AlertMgmt -> Thresh : Create threshold
Thresh -> DB : Store threshold
DB --> Thresh : Confirmation

AlertMgmt -> Audit : Log action

Thresh -> Analyst : Notify new threshold
Analyst -> Algo : Update algorithms
Algo -> Audit : Log update

SensorRep -> Rec : Submit recommendation
Rec -> DB : Store recommendation

@enduml